rules_elixir_mix
=============

This repository is derived from and adapts work from:

* Discord rules_elixir
  https://github.com/discord/rules_elixir
  Baseline inspected/adapted from commit c8b30e5
  ("[mix_release] ensure priv/ is copied after compile/priv split (#27)").

* RabbitMQ rules_elixir
  https://github.com/rabbitmq/rules_elixir
  Discord rules_elixir is a fork of RabbitMQ rules_elixir.

* RabbitMQ rules_erlang
  https://github.com/rabbitmq/rules_erlang
  Provider, Rebar, and Erlang/OTP source-build patterns were inspected and
  selectively adapted. It is not a Bazel or runtime dependency.

